[[大卫·希利|大卫·希利]]是北爱尔兰退役[[足球|足球]]运动员，曾于2000至2013年代表[[北爱尔兰足球代表队|北爱尔兰足球代表队]]参赛。在此期间他共参与95场国际赛事并打入36球，成为北爱尔兰头号射手。<ref name="rsssf">{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150906192509/http://rsssf.com/miscellaneous/dhealy-intlg.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.rsssf.com/miscellaneous/dhealy-intlg.html | title = David Healy – Goals in international matches | first = Roberto | last = Mamrud | publisher = Rec.Sport.Soccer Statistics Foundation | date = 2013-09-05 | accessdate = 2020-07-24 | archivedate = 2015-09-06 }}</ref>2000年2月，他首次走上国际赛场，在[[若西·巴特尔体育场|若西·巴特尔体育场]]举办的[[热身赛|友谊赛]]迎战[[卢森堡国家足球队|卢森堡队]]并打进两球，最终北爱尔兰队以3比1获胜<ref name="first">{{cite news | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/sport/football/654391.stm | title = Healy gives McIlroy perfect start | publisher = [[英国广播公司新闻|BBC News]] | date = 2000-02-23 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200303230720/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/sport/football/654391.stm | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-07-24 | archivedate = 2020-03-03 }}</ref>。2004年6月，他在对阵[[千里达及托巴哥国家足球队|千里达及托巴哥队]]的友谊赛打入职业生涯的第14个国际进球，-{打}-破[[比利·吉莱斯皮|比利·吉莱斯皮]]（{{lang|en|Billy Gillespie}}）与[[科林·克拉克|科林·克拉克]]（{{lang|en|Colin Clarke}}）共同保持的13球纪录，成为北爱尔兰历史头号射手<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.irishfa.com/international/squad-profiles/profile/2036/billy-gillespie/ | publisher = Irish Football Association | title = Profile of Billy Gillespie | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160307184449/http://www.irishfa.com/international/squad-profiles/profile/2036/billy-gillespie/ | archivedate = 2016-03-07 | deadurl = yes | access-date = 2020-07-24 }}</ref>。截至2015年10月，[[凯尔·拉弗蒂|凯尔·拉弗蒂]]以16球成为仅次于希利的北爱尔兰二号射手<ref>{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180930235802/https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/international/kyle-lafferty-gives-northern-irish-a-reason-to-believe-10142483.html | archivedate = 2018-09-30 | deadurl = no | url = https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/international/kyle-lafferty-gives-northern-irish-a-reason-to-believe-10142483.html | title = Kyle Lafferty gives Northern Irish a reason to believe | last = Walker | first = Michael | newspaper = The Independent | location = London | date = 2015-03-30 | accessdate = 2020-07-24 }}</ref>。2012年，希利在[[2014年国际足协世界杯外围赛|2014年国际足协世界杯资格赛]]对阵[[阿塞拜疆国家足球队|阿塞拜疆队]]时打入他的第36颗国际进球，此前他已连续四年粒球未进，但这也是他职业生涯中最后一次在国际赛场得分<ref>{{cite news | url = https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/sport/football/healy-happy-to-be-back-on-the-mark-28923152.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180930235803/https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/sport/football/healy-happy-to-be-back-on-the-mark-28923152.html | title = Healy happy to be back on the mark | newspaper = Belfast Telegraph | date = 2012-11-15 | accessdate = 2020-07-24 | archivedate = 2018-09-30 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

希利是北爱尔兰唯一在国际比赛两次达成[[帽子戏法|帽子戏法]]的足球运动员<ref name="iconic" />，两次都是[[2008年欧洲足球锦标赛外围赛|2008年欧洲足球锦标赛外围赛]]，分别是2006年9月对阵[[西班牙国家足球队|西班牙队]]，球队最终就靠他的三颗进球以3比2险胜<ref name="firsthat">{{cite web | archivedate = 2018-04-06 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180406092046/http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuro/season=2008/matches/round=2241/match=83713/postmatch/report/index.html | date = 2006-09-07 | accessdate = 2018-04-06 | publisher = UEFA | url = http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuro/season=2008/matches/round=2241/match=83713/postmatch/report/index.html | title = Healy hat-trick humbles Spain }}</ref>；另一次是六个月后帮助球队以4比1大胜[[列支敦士登国家足球队|列支敦士登队]]<ref name="secondhat">{{cite news | publisher = BBC Sport | date = 2007-03-24 | accessdate = 2020-07-24 | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/6473569.stm | archivedate = 2019-08-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190827183058/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/6473569.stm | title = Liechtenstein 1–4 N Ireland | deadurl = no }}</ref>。同时，希利在2008年欧洲足球锦标赛外围赛共13次攻破对手大门，比其他任何国家球员都多<ref name="iconic">{{cite web | archivedate = 2018-04-05 | accessdate = 2018-04-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180405184825/http://www.uefa.com/memberassociations/news/newsid=2031967.html | url = http://www.uefa.com/memberassociations/news/newsid=2031967.html | title = Euro record-holder Healy announces retirement | last = Fullerton | first = Darren | publisher = UEFA | date = 2013-12-03 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>，为此[[米歇尔·普拉蒂尼|米歇尔·普拉蒂尼]]代表[[欧洲足球协会联盟|欧洲足球协会联盟]]向他授予特别奖<ref>{{cite news | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180930235832/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/7313734.stm | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/7313734.stm | title = Platini honours NI striker Healy | publisher = BBC Sport | date = 2008-03-26 | accessdate = 2015-09-12 | archivedate = 2018-09-30 }}</ref>。希利的纪录一直保持到2015年10月，才被[[波兰国家足球队|波兰队]]射手[[罗伯特·莱万多夫斯基|罗伯特·莱万多夫斯基]]在[[2016年欧洲足球锦标赛|2016年欧洲足球锦标赛]]对抗[[爱尔兰国家足球队|爱尔兰队]]时追平<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuro/qualifiers/news/newsid=2292506.html | title = Lewandowski equals Healy's scoring record | publisher = UEFA | date = 2015-10-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151114015938/http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuro/qualifiers/news/newsid=2292506.html | archivedate = 2015-11-14 | deadurl = yes | access-date = 2020-07-24 }}</ref>。

北爱尔兰队在希利效力期间始终未能打入国际足协世界杯或欧洲足球锦标赛，他的大部分入球都是资格赛上取得，友谊赛反倒很少<ref name="rsssf" />。希利是列支敦士登征战国际的头号大敌，共五次破门，他的大半入球（20个）是在[[贝尔法斯特|贝尔法斯特]]的[[温莎公园|温莎公园]]取得<ref name="rsssf" />。希利退役后，北爱尔兰队经理[[米高·奧尼爾_(足球員)|米高·奧尼爾]]称赞他是北爱尔兰“标志球员”<ref name="iconic" />。
